Description: Handle of Rhodian pottery transport amphora. Rectangular stamp
Curator's comments: Only known from Petrie's drawing in his Journal, 1884-5, p.110, 25. It is not clear whether this is a separate entry or is to be taken with 24. Name, Archokrates.
Bibliographic references: Villing et al 2013-2015 / Naukratis: Greeks in Egypt (JB.0749)
